    "gp_section_547415757596853111": {
      "settings": {
        "checksum": "3d6eda389f425faf549a389d36e4f3c768ae4d8fff98a8d8d9ed9d984f008cda_1_1_0_0__1",
        "gg-n9gr3-oK_label": "<p>Step 1</p>",
        "gg-vMdwPnao_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-e3261c34-ae51-414c-81dd-4e9edf9e512a.png",
        "gg2fynqfSWV_label": "<p>Check Availability Now...</p>",
        "gg2s3Fu3z9K_text": "<p>The SmoothSpine pillow is designed to be used in between your legs, stays with you all night, and doesn’t take up any additional space in bed.&nbsp;</p>",
        "gg3N9tzoou2_text": "<p>Yes - SmoothSpine understands that everyone has different-sized legs.</p>",
        "gg3lLzTDdOS_text": "<p>Designed with Leading PT Specialists and Trusted by Sleep Experts Nationwide</p>",
        "gg3qXa6I1vg_text": "<p>SmoothSpine will be delivered to your door (orders ship from our local warehouse within 24 hours on average).</p>",
        "gg4JFz99Gy3_text": "<p><strong><u>The Soft Secure Elastic Strap</u></strong> keeps the pillow perfectly in place all night even when you turn over.</p>",
        "gg4bAuuAWVP_text": "<p>In fact, many of our users report that it helps improve their recovery by keeping their spine aligned and reducing pressure on the joints.</p>",
        "gg541QMMpZW_text": "<p>The SmoothSpine Alignment Pillow is a revolutionary leg pillow that <strong>helps you eliminate hip and back pain, reduce sciatic nerve pressure, and improve sleep quality</strong> all without needing invasive surgery or relying on harmful pills.</p>",
        "gg5AnEyK174_text": "How Do I Use the SmoothSpine Pillow?",
        "gg5BgFAsbXG_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-e2b3d586-3cbb-4c88-a754-1f1298f69f98.png",
        "gg5hZqy7Vzl_text": "<p>In the highly unlikely event that you are not satisfied with your purchase, SmoothSpine offers a <strong>90-night money back guarantee on ALL purchases.</strong></p>",
        "gg6V_sIyQGh_text": "It’s Time to Finally Eliminate Your Back &amp; Hip Pain (And Sleep Pain-Free Through The Night)",
        "gg6YYGqGoMJ_text": "<p>Simply put the soft, comfortable strap around your leg when you go to bed and let the <strong>“Active Spine Realignment™</strong> stimulate the natural healing process in your hips and back - so you can sleep, run, and jump out of bed without pain holding you back.</p>",
        "gg7eN2QIiHW_text": "<p>Ever since SmoothSpine was released to the public earlier this year, an incredible amount of buzz has been generated. Due to its popularity and positive reviews, the company is so confident in their product that they are offering a limited time discount up to 55% this month only.</p>",
        "gg7gtrWtUJ__text": "<p>We’ve worked hard to offer this breakthrough design at a competitive price, without markups as <strong>we know how expensive other solutions</strong> are such as surgery, weekly physiotherapy sessions, and the constant cost of pain meds.</p>",
        "ggAKiS2EISn_text": "Can I Use SmoothSpine With Larger Legs?",
        "ggBL5BK-s6P_html5Url": "https://cdn.shopify.com/videos/c/o/v/39f6fe7cde8742cca28579d72d75ec06.mp4",
        "ggBL5BK-s6P_vimeoUrl": "https://vimeo.com/347119375",
        "ggBL5BK-s6P_youtubeUrl": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cyzh48XRS4M",
        "ggBzc-BUFzk_text": "Eliminate Back &amp; Hip Pain: One Simple Pillow<br>Realigns Your Spine While You Sleep",
        "ggCR9pMNf_P_text": "With SmoothSpine, getting started is easy:",
        "ggDF1U9uOJJ_text": "Is SmoothSpine Safe?",
        "ggEUHj4HmHo_text": "<p>It really is that simple!</p>",
        "ggEh76kowP9_text": "<p>, Ever since SmoothSpine was released to the public earlier</p>",
        "ggEq3zcOzTs_text": "How Does the SmoothSpine Pillow Work?",
        "ggFG6AdGk0q_text": "<p>Many people have tried to sleep with an old pillow between their legs, often failing to get the results they want.</p>",
        "ggGw9gxZhIQ_text": "How Fast Can I See Results?",
        "ggHgs612zsq_text": "<p>This means that you have up to 90 days from the time your order arrives at your door to try it, and see how it works for you...</p>",
        "ggIV0LUdnWf_text": "<p>You either lose it at night, don’t support your body in the right areas, or simply get annoyed by how big and awkward it is.</p>",
        "ggIsN89vVry_text": "<p>“Before SmoothSpine, I couldn’t sleep for more than 2-3 hours. Now I’m sleeping a good 6-7 and getting out of bed easily in the morning! <strong>It's given me my life back.”</strong></p>",
        "ggJafmEGs4q_text": "Relieve Hip &amp; Back Pain Today!",
        "ggJc2kPVK5Y_label": "<p>Step 3</p>",
        "ggK204xJqMx_text": "<p>It is designed to support <strong>your lower body and stays comfortably between your legs with the secure elastic strap,</strong> making it convenient and easy to use no matter how much you toss and turn.</p>",
        "ggK3g4lxCnC_text": "<p>~ Linda Giles, Verified Customer</p>",
        "ggK7Z8rtqQe_customText": "As Of",
        "ggKOQZwDDdJ_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-03141a6c-9e72-42aa-a1a0-b85d00db85c4.png",
        "ggLCedvH6h6_text": "<p>A Special Offer for Our Readers:</p>",
        "ggLSHdiIV3P_text": "<p>The SmoothSpine Pillow uses <strong>“Active Spine Realignment™</strong> to stimulate the natural healing process in your hips and back <strong>allowing users to live and sleep pain-free without the need for going under the knife!</strong></p>",
        "ggMF9JucNys_text": "<p>~ Rita Cowles, Verified Customer</p>",
        "ggN7S5tmqzD_html5Url": "https://cdn.shopify.com/videos/c/o/v/172158b2b09247fe9bc693def5723e21.mp4",
        "ggN7S5tmqzD_vimeoUrl": "https://vimeo.com/347119375",
        "ggN7S5tmqzD_youtubeUrl": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cyzh48XRS4M",
        "ggOeoq5KSo3_text": "What Is the SmoothSpine Alignment Pillow?",
        "ggPVHsBMDSV_text": "<p>If you're tired of struggling with chronic back and hip pain, lack of mobility, and feeling like a burden on your spouse and family then <u>SmoothSpine is exactly what you need.</u></p>",
        "ggPcNXDSciV_text": "Will the SmoothSpine Pillow Help With Sciatica?",
        "ggQC5Rx9hMa_text": "<p>Using the SmoothSpine Pillow is as simple as it gets - all you have to do is slide it around your legs and get comfortable in bed.</p>",
        "ggQHvkrfTNZ_text": "<p>The pillow features three scientifically-designed elements that work together:</p>",
        "ggQxiPyCW7k_label": "<p>Check Availability &gt;&gt;</p>",
        "ggR1WQJD4UZ_text": "<p>The SmoothSpine Pillow is available exclusively through our <a href=\"https://smoothspine.com/products/pres-alp\"><span style=\"color:#0056B3;\">official website.</span></a></p>",
        "ggRqpnTAU1D_text": "<p>Check availability and take advantage of our discount link by clicking below!</p>",
        "ggS3GePHfon_text": "How Is This Different Than Using A Regular Pillow?",
        "ggSLY_ACEPl_text": "<p>If for any reason you are not happy or you have not experienced a complete transformation in your sleep, hip, and spinal health simply reach out to our helpful customer support team at <strong>support@smoothspine.com</strong> and they will issue you a <strong>FULL refund - No questions asked!</strong></p>",
        "ggTIWMF6Doa_text": "<p>The SmoothSpine Pillow will deliver results during the first night of use, of course, your hips and back will not magically be healed after 1 night however <strong>most users experience less pain and better sleep after just 1 night.</strong></p>",
        "ggU0SWLogHk_text": "<p>this year, an incredible amount of buzz has been generated. Due to its popularity and positive reviews, the company is so confident in their product that they are offering a limited time discount up to 55% this month only.</p>",
        "ggVEPAomqLy_text": "What If I Am Not Happy With My Purchase?",
        "ggWJdOpfCQe_text": "Eliminate Back &amp; Hip Pain: One Simple Pillow Realigns Your Spine While You Sleep",
        "ggYqGMUAujz_text": "<p>This results in longer lasting relief, uninterrupted sleep, and more comfort.</p>",
        "ggZlJRJg2fH_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-ef8e5b77-645c-42bd-84ee-13b3623df084.png",
        "gg_a6Dv-FT3_text": "<p>That’s why the elastic strap is designed to fit comfortably around all leg sizes, so no matter how small or large your legs may be we can guarantee a comfortable fit.</p>",
        "gg_ci_s3UbB_text": "<p>Enter your shipping and billing information on the secure checkout and we will begin to pack your order and send it out the very next day.</p>",
        "gg_fgIh0ti9_text": "<p><strong>“My life took a 180 after SmoothSpine</strong> - my doctor recommended it after a scan of my hips and spine. I wish she’d given it to me years ago, <strong>I even cancelled my chiro appointments.</strong> My husband is amazed.”</p>",
        "gg_pY699Tzg_text": "<p><strong><u>The High Density Memory Foam</u></strong> is comfortably thick to perfectly support your top leg keeping your hips parallel and relieving pressure on your joints.</p>",
        "ggaJ4lx1Jaz_text": "<p>50% discount on this product - only during the launch phase through this link</p>",
        "ggavy2anxq-_text": "<p>SmoothSpine is being used by thousands of side sleepers and is backed by Dr. Adam Story a spine and pain specialist for over 10 years - It has been determined that SmoothSpine is 100% safe!</p>",
        "ggb_ZMb46rq_text": "<p>SmoothSpine is not available in stores and please do not fall victim to cheap knockoffs - SmoothSpine is a scientifically designed device, and just as you wouldn’t take pain medication without knowing its ingredients, you shouldn’t use a device without understanding how or where it was created.</p>",
        "ggbtx4NzI9c_text": "<p>From here all you have to do is slightly adjust the placement that is most comfortable for you.</p>",
        "ggdQHB865BQ_text": "<p>100% - The SmoothSpine Alignment Pillow is designed to be gentle and supportive, making it perfectly safe to use after a knee or hip replacement.</p>",
        "ggdYXgWfB6X_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-46f9b304-f463-4cd8-aa6c-a5f932bd4518.png",
        "ggeBMVuQeJz_label": "<p>Step 2</p>",
        "ggepQZyukxE_text": "Where Can I Purchase the SmoothSpine Pillow?",
        "ggfEelyLkSE_text": "<p>Our goal is to eliminate all of those costs and instead, <strong>you just need a one-time payment for SmoothSpine</strong> which usually retails at $69.95 however there is a massive sale until midnight where you can get SmoothSpine for as low as $29.95 when you select the biggest bundle.</p>",
        "gggQrcKucaY_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-e9871aa4-1181-48d4-97bf-266694e17765.webp",
        "gghoVeGaVVR_text": "<p>After using SmoothSpine for 7 nights you should experience almost complete relief from hip, back and leg pain - your nights sleep should be back to normal and your joints should feel decades younger in the morning.</p>",
        "ggiIc82ngmW_label": "<p>Step 4</p>",
        "ggixnIcXtIv_text": "Claim Your SmoothSpine Now and Save 50% Off Until Midnight",
        "ggjYkdFkXhk_label": "<p>Check Discounts &amp; Availability</p>",
        "ggjaqFOYTBo_text": "<p>At SmoothSpine we are committed to <strong>making long-term pain relief affordable and accessible for anyone who needs it.</strong></p>",
        "ggjd3yLzY2V_html5Url": "https://cdn.shopify.com/videos/c/o/v/58b42102010b4a9598f9f2ebc2bccd38.mp4",
        "ggjd3yLzY2V_vimeoUrl": "https://vimeo.com/347119375",
        "ggjd3yLzY2V_youtubeUrl": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cyzh48XRS4M",
        "ggkAgovtx0b_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-06dbebf9-9c7a-4887-bb3b-0dd2a5c315fc.jpg",
        "ggkQa2qKlTA_customText": "As Of",
        "gglhBQY9Fds_text": "<p>Finally, allow SmoothSpine to turn your sleepless nights and painful joints into a feeling of bliss and relaxation.</p>",
        "ggn-HrkzObE_text": "<p>Claim Your SmoothSpine Now and SAVE 50% OFF</p>",
        "ggnh0HmgcCI_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-4676e7eb-aa4f-472e-8436-3b8dc689efaf.png",
        "ggp1rRGlpGy_text": "<p><strong><u>The Unique Contour Shape</u></strong> gives you the optimal amount of support and keeps your spine naturally aligned to prevent nerve compression and twisting.</p>",
        "ggqJoxWzxHh_text": "<p>Click the \"Check Availability\" button below to check if we still have stock (Due to high demand we sell out fast…)</p>",
        "ggrIon6KC7T_text": "<p>Absolutely - The majority of our customers purchase SmoothSpine because they suffer from persisent cases of Sciatica and have been told their only option is spinal surgery or months of expensive treatments.&nbsp;</p>",
        "ggs4PwTGdHp_text": "<p>~ Charles Russell, Verified Customer</p>",
        "ggsZCE5ou7S_text": "Is It Safe To Use After A Knee Or Hip Replacement?",
        "ggsiuTHrMRy_text": "<p>By stabilizing your hips and lower back while you sleep, the pillow prevents unnecessary strain on your replacement joint, allowing your body to heal naturally and comfortably.&nbsp;</p>",
        "ggv-34H59h7_text": "<p>And with our competitive prices, responsive support team, and commitment to your success, you can trust <strong>SmoothSpine to support you on every step of your knee pain journey!</strong></p>",
        "ggvfxh-DOVf_text": "How Much Does SmoothSpine Cost?",
        "ggwd-sUAAXx_text": "<p>So if you're ready to turn back the clock on your hips and back and start living without the constant stabbing pain, <strong><u>click \"Check Availability\" now, and let's begin transforming your day and nights today!</u></strong></p>",
        "ggwjqx_XcKu_text": "<p>“SmoothSpine is <strong>way cheaper</strong> than anything else I’ve tried in the past. My doctor was considering spinal surgery for me, but now she says <strong>I’ve realigned my spine and hips</strong> and I don’t need it!”</p>",
        "ggxUX5yAt3-_text": "<p>if we have stock you will land on our secure checkout where you can choose the bundle that best suits your needs (The bigger the bundle the more $ you save).</p>",
        "ggxeiti_fLd_text": "Take advantage of our discount by clicking the link below!",
        "ggyWKKy3GSm_text": "<p>Designed with Leading PT Specialists and Trusted by</p><p>Sleep Experts Nationwide</p>"
      },
